text
@<HTML>

<HEAD>
<TITLE>The Gran Turismo Pit Stop - Arcade - Extras</TITLE>
</HEAD>


<BODY bgcolor="#FFFFFF" text="#000000">

<CENTER>
<H1> 
The Gran Turismo Pit Stop<BR>
Arcade - Extras
</H1>
<H3>
</H3>
</CENTER>
<P>
<BR><BR>
<HR>
<BR>

<OL>
  <LI> Win at each of the arcade tracks with all 3 classes of cars.  (A, B & C)
       Doing so on each track opens up a particular extra track.
       <UL TYPE=DOT>
       <LI>High Speed Ring unlocks Autumn Ring
       <LI>Trial Mountain unlocks Deep Forest
       <LI>Grand Valley East unlocks Special Stage R5
       <LI>Clubman R5 unlocks Grand Valley Speedway
       </UL><BR></LI>
  <LI> Win at each of the extra arcade tracks with all 3 classes of cars.
	Doing so on each extra track unlocks a different manufacturer.
	The 4 manufacturers are Toyota, Subaru, Dodge, & TVR, and
        are unlocked in that order regardless of the order in which
        you complete the extra tracks. (Note: hidden cars can be unlocked
        before you have unlocked all the hidden tracks).
       <BR><BR></LI>
  <LI> By winning all 8 tracks using all 3 classes of cars on the Normal
	level, the staff credit movie is displayed.  This is now also
	accessible from the menus.
       <BR><BR></LI>
  <LI> By winning all 8 tracks using all 3 classes of cars on the Difficult
	level, the "GT Hi-Res" mode is accessible from the menus. 
       </LI>
</OL>


<P><BR>



<HR>
